1. *Čiste* ruke su važne za održavanje higijene. (Clean hands are important for maintaining hygiene.)
2. Ja *čistim* kuću svake nedelje. (I clean the house every week.)
3. Oni su *čistili* kuhinju kada sam došao kući. (They were cleaning the kitchen when I came home.)
4. *Čisti* vazduh je neophodan za zdravlje ljudi. (Clean air is necessary for human health.)
5. Oni su me *čistili* odgovornosti koja nije bila moja. (They cleared me of responsibility that wasn't mine.)
6. *Čista* savest je bitna za miran san. (A clear conscience is important for peaceful sleep.)
7. Ja *čistim* zube posle svakog obroka. (I brush my teeth after every meal.)
8. Ona je *čistila* kupatilo celo popodne. (She was cleaning the bathroom all afternoon.)
9. *Čist* papir je potreban za štampanje dokumenata. (Clean paper is necessary for printing documents.)
10. Oni su *očistili* ulicu od smeća. (They cleaned the street from garbage.)